text: Customized data aggregation reports are run either as scheduled or on demand. The kept and unkept records gives an overview of how many UDRs currently exist in aggregation storage and how many UDRs that have been consolidated. The balance should only be zero when no more files have been processed and all aggregated data have been timed out.
title: Data Aggregation Reports - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
